Finalized data include the profiles of temperature, salinity, oxygen saturation, and fluorescense.  Most hydrocast stations are near atolls and islands and typically reach to 500 m.  Shallow casts can be of much shorter range.       </abstract>    <purpose>         Understand the physical characteristics for better interpretation of ecosystem dynamics       </purpose>
